ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Tile
ObjectStates.Nickname: [b]C O N C E A L  /  R E V E A L  [/b]
ObjectStates.Description:
[b]Warp Charge 6
[b]Conceal:[/b] Choose a friendly [b]ASURYANI INFANTRY[/b] or [b]ASURYANI BIKER[/b] within 18". Your opponent must subtract 1 from all hit rolls for ranged weapons that target that unit until your next Psychic phase.
[b]Reveal:[/b] Choose an enemy unit within 18" of the psyker. It does not gain any bonus to its saving throws for being in cover until your next psychic phase.

ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Tile
ObjectStates.Nickname: [b]E M B O L D E N  /  H O R R I F Y
ObjectStates.Description:
[b]Warp Charge 6
[b]Embolden:[/b] Choose a friendly [b]ASURYANI INFANTRY[/b] or [b]ASURYANI BIKER[/b] unit within 18" of the psyker  add 2 to the Leadership characteristics of that unit until your next
Psychic phase. 
[b]Horrify:[/b] Choose an enemy unit within 18" of the psyker  your opponent must subtract 1 from the Leadership of that unit until your next Psychic phase.

ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Tile
ObjectStates.Nickname: [b]P R O T E C T  /  J I N X
ObjectStates.Description:
[b]Warp Charge 7
[b]Protect:[/b] Choose a friendly [b]ASURYANI INFANTRY[/b] or [b]ASURYANI BIKER[/b] unit within 18" of the psyker  add 1 to the saving throws made for that unit until your next Psychic phase. 
[b]Jinx:[/b] Choose an enemy unit within 18" of the psyker  your opponent must subtract 1 from all saving throws made for that unit until your next Psychic phase.

ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Tile
ObjectStates.Nickname: [b]Q U I C K E N  /  R E S T R A I N
ObjectStates.Description:
[b]Warp Charge 7
[b]Quicken:[/b] Choose a friendly [b]ASURYANI INFANTRY[/b] or [b]ASURYANI BIKER[/b] unit within 18" of the psyker. That unit can immediately move as if it were the Movement phase.
[b]Restrain:[/b] Choose an enemy unit within 18" of the psyker  your opponent must halve the Move characteristic of all model in that unit until your next Psychic phase.

ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Tile
ObjectStates.Nickname: [b]E M P O W E R  /  E N E R V A T E
ObjectStates.Description:
[b]Warp Charge 6
[b]Empower:[/b] Choose a friendly [b]ASURYANI INFANTRY[/b] or [b]ASURYANI BIKER[/b] unit within 18" of the psyker. Add 1 to wound
rolls in the Fight phase for that unit until your next Psychic phase. 
[b]Enervate:[/b] Choose an enemy unit within 18" of the psyker  your opponent must subtract 1 from all wound rolls made in the Fight phase until your next Psychic Phase
